Program: Discovery
Title: Recreating the Earth's magnetic field
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrwhx
Last Broadcast Date: 28 September 1995
How two geophysicists have recreated the Earth's core using a supercomputer. The scientists have used the experiment to re-create the Earth's magnetic field. Also in the programme, engineering new drugs using cyberspace and the paeleontologists who are studying newly discovered coprolites in Wales.